@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ecqulk(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (wp.abs(wp.exp(tmp + 0.25)) / v1)
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.exp(wp.abs(v2 + 0.18)))
    tmp = 0.65
    v1 = ((v1 * 0.16) * wp.cos(v0))
    v1 = tmp
    v0 = v0
    v2 = wp.abs((0.04 / tmp))
    tmp = 0.47
    data[tid] = v0
